name: Reform Lines
description: This is a chart of history and yet-to-be-fulfilled prophecy which is based off of studies from the KJV Bible, Ellen White's writings, and an interpretation of Current events with "William Miller's 14 Rules of Prophetic Interpretation". This knowledge is subject to update and is current as of 09/06/2021. It has been published to make it easier to be used as a part of a larger web project and consequently is open to the public within the Figma community as well.
